title: High school football: York stays alive in hunt for postseason
text:
High school football: York stays alive in hunt for postseason Published: Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015 5:30 a.m. CDT By SUBURBAN LIFE MEDIA 
HILLSIDE â€“ York football took a step in the right direction in its quest for a playoff berth with a 43-10 win against Proviso West on Oct. 9. 
With the win, the Dukes improved to 3-4 overall and 1-3 in the West Suburban Silver. 
York is on the road against on Oct. 16 to face fellow 3-4 team Downers Grove North.
